{"tid":1973489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無視原廠硬出　Cooking Mama 新作變「侵權媽媽」！","createTime":"2020-04-15T08:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T15:53:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":112,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"603d2622041d0c221a3b60db6fe452918bf3f221","tid":1973489,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"在月初時於 Switch 及 PS4 上推出的《 Cooking Mama :  Cookstar 》，雖然不及《動物森友會》的人氣高，但依然吸引一班老 Fans 去購買遊戲。剛才 Cooking Mama 的版權持有方 Office Create 就發表聲明，指《 Cookstar 》的開發商無視了他們的要求，強行推出遊戲，屬侵權行為。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www-pcmarket-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/cooking-mama-cookstar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-pcmarket-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fcooking-mama-cookstar.jpg&h=1e1632ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自去年底遊戲一直未有推出日期，但於 3 月時卻無聲無息推出市面，原來背後有著這樣的故事。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提到於 2018 年的時候遊戲原出版商 Office Create 批准了遊戲廠商 Planet Entertainment （下稱  Planet ）開發《 Cooking Mama 》的新作（即後來的《 Cookstar 》），但因為所交出的成品未達標準， Office Create 就多次要求 Planet 修改直至達標，然而 Planet 卻無視原廠要求直接發行了《 Cooking Mama :  Cookstar 》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www-pcmarket-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/771713fa-0244-4957-a8c9-23857786aee4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-pcmarket-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F771713fa-0244-4957-a8c9-23857786aee4.png&h=8cb322ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到 3DS 版本時，原廠 Office Create 依然負責開發及發行<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，本來 Office Create 與 Planet 所簽下的協議，只許可他們推出 Nintendo Switch 版的遊戲，但  Planet 卻再度違約，私下開發了遊戲的 PS4 版《 Cooking Mama :  Cookstar 》並推出。<br />\n<br />\nOffice Create 發現事情後，就於 3 月 30 日終止與 Planet 的合約，但 Planet 繼續在其網站上廣告和銷售未經授權的《  Cookstar 》，故意侵犯 Office Create 的權利。 Office Create 對 Planet 行為感到失望，正在計劃針對 Planet 提出法律訴訟，以保護所有玩家以及《 Cooking Mama 》系列。<br />\n<br />\n順提一帶，在遊戲推出當日有玩家指出 Planet 在《 Cookstar 》遊戲裡暗藏加密貨幣程式，利用玩家的主機挖礦，導致 Switch  機身過熱。雖然官方於 Twitter 上極力否認事實。但發售日當天，遊戲在 Nintendo eShop 僅僅上架數小時後便被全數刪除，令人懷疑可能與指控有關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www-pcmarket-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/EU2oaWvWoAAmOAV-710x844.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-pcmarket-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FEU2oaWvWoAAmOAV-710x844.jpg&h=3574b594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推出當日時玩家指控 Planet 利用主機挖礦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2020/04/15/%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E5%8E%9F%E5%BB%A0%E7%A1%AC%E5%87%BA-cooking-mama%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C%E8%AE%8A%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E5%2587%25BA-cooking-mama%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%25AE%258A%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25AA%25BD%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQLyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=cf0ee80c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2020/04/15/%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E5%8E%9F%E5%BB%A0%E7%A1%AC%E5%87%BA-cooking-mama%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C%E8%AE%8A%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD/</a>"},{"pid":"d4def09d92e6df1aee65b71eab438130ac7b50dc","tid":1973489,"uid":28114,"like":131,"dislike":0,"score":131,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"要變絕版game喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf15ab8286a65795e4aaae9e4d60a930077ff85","tid":1973489,"uid":3405,"like":166,"dislike":1,"score":165,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁都格硬出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6adaab